<h1>Indian Food</h1>
<p>Indian cuisine is a vibrant tapestry of flavors and traditions, with each region offering its own unique dishes. From
the spicy curries of the South to the rich Mughlai dishes of the North, Indian food is a celebration of diversity and
cultural heritage.</p>
